Garment Changelog
=================

Version 0.5
Released: March 25th, 2014

* Added a user@host tag to each release
* Roles are now optional
* Allow for include or exclude of steps during deploy so that you can skip
  certain steps if you know you don't need them.

Version 0.4.1
Released: March 17th, 2014

* Improved the cleanup function


Version: 0.4
Released: March 16th, 2014

* Added the ability to Extend configuration environments
* Fixed the 'deploy' script
